nodes.text: The NTB-630 naval bomber, also known as the NTB-630 bomber, was a model of bomber used by the Republic Navy during the Clone Wars. Like the PTB-625 planetary bomber, it was a joint production by Incom Corporation and Subpro Corporation, and the Galactic Republic often used the vessel the Outer Rim. Jedi Master Wom-Nii Gnaden used a NTB-630 during the Battle of Crombach Nebula.
